    {
        "content": "<p>It would be nice to have strong version of <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/Mathlib/Data/Int/Init.html#Int.inductionOn'\">Int.inductionOn'</a>, this would be useful here to prove this for all <code>x</code>, not just positive.</p>",
        "id": 566123218,
        "sender_full_name": "Jakub Nowak",
        "timestamp": 1767415046
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>oh, looks like this one is avoiding the casting</p>",
        "id": 566123488,
